  <body>
    <section name="Logging">
      <p>
       Whinstone provides logging information through the use of 
       Simple Logging Facade for Java or (SLF4J) serves as a simple facade or 
       abstraction for various logging frameworks, e.g. java.util.logging, log4j and 
       logback, allowing the end user to plug in the desired logging framework at deployment time. 
       </p>
       
       <p>
       <a href="http://www.slf4j.org/">More information.</a>
       </p> 
    </section>
